Contents

  My personal vim configuration. The following plugins are included (as submodules):
  - command-t - https://github.com/wincent/command-t.git
  - Fugitive - https://github.com/tpope/vim-fugitive
  - pyflakes - https://github.com/vim-scripts/pyflakes.vim
  - fswitch - https://github.com/vim-scripts/FSwitch
  - vim-project - https://github.com/amiorin/vim-project
  - lightline - https://github.com/itchyny/lightline.vim
  - asyncrun.vim - https://github.com/skywind3000/asyncrun.vim.git
  - simplenote.vim - https://github.com/mrtazz/simplenote.vim


Installation
  
  To clone the repository, execute the following commands:

    mkdir ~/.vim
    git clone https://github.com/derteta/vim-config.git ~/.vim
    cd ~/.vim
    git submodule update --init --recursive

  Now call the setup script to integrate the configuration in your environment:

    ./setup.sh
